    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "Solid good-condition example that appears complete, presentable, and ready to enjoy as a driver. It shows well overall with decent paint, trim, and interior, and it comes across as a car that has been maintained and kept usable rather than freshly restored. Expect a clean, honest older car with some age-related cosmetic wear and minor imperfections if you look closely, but nothing that takes away from its overall appeal as a nice driver.",
