      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Clean, good-condition car that should make a solid choice for someone wanting a well-kept driver without expecting a showpiece. It presents nicely overall, with a body, paint, trim, and glass that show well from a normal viewing distance, though you should expect some typical age-related cosmetic wear and minor imperfections on closer inspection. The interior appears tidy and cared for, and overall it gives the impression of a vehicle that has been maintained and enjoyed rather than neglected. A buyer can expect a presentable, honest car that is above average for its age, but not mint or flawless.",
      "price": 34900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and full of potential, this vehicle offers an affordable way into dependable transportation. It shows its age and is best suited for a buyer who values price, practicality, and the chance to put their own touch on it. A straightforward value option for commuting, a backup vehicle, or a project purchase.",
