      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable car with plenty of life left for the right person? This one isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest little vehicle that could make a great budget commuter, first car, or weekend project. It starts, drives, and offers a lot of value for someone who wants dependable basic transport without spending a fortune. If you\u2019re practical and don\u2019t mind giving it a bit of TLC, there\u2019s a lot to like here.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Strong-running used car with solid bones and plenty of usable life left for the right buyer. It shows its age cosmetically and will need attention in spots, but the powertrain pulls well, the transmission engages as it should, and it remains a practical budget-friendly driver or ideal starter project. A good option for someone who appreciates mechanical simplicity and wants affordable transportation with upside.",
      "price": 5950.0,
